{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"162851-emotions-come-and-go","title":"Emotions Come and Go","description":"Look out for the emotions you feel and why! ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mimi  Werna"],"illustrators":["Joe Werna"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/162851-emotions-come-and-go"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/231859/size3/bdb9d057c77432781e3e911d92aa1bfe.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/231859/size6/bdb9d057c77432781e3e911d92aa1bfe.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228044/size6/e05e3298c63fd98e793ef3d16597d05e.jpg","text":"Ada is chuckling because she heard a funny story. \nShe is smiling. \nWhat is Ada feeling?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228045/size6/70edab905ab1ebd900411cab6c57359d.jpg","text":"Gisa is feeling grumpy. \nHe has a scowl on his face. \nWhy is he irritated?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228046/size6/8220d7713caebd20a0f86cd09bc8cb61.jpg","text":"Yuadoo is scared of the dark. \nEveryone feels fear sometimes. \nBut Yuadoo can ask for help.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228047/size6/efcd761c459a3126ba04f98828d24ede.jpg","text":"Chidubem is worried about his school work. \nHe can tell his teacher. \nHe can ask for help.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228048/size6/bc819c082a4f41dccb4b21e93ea81946.jpg","text":"Lushan is playing around! \nIt's okay to be silly sometimes.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228050/size6/3c5a058cd7e0147da6785678c67ecadf.jpg","text":"Eruro is feeling sad. \nIt's okay to cry. \nEmotions come and go.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228052/size6/1ff21c2d2c42e5dc8ec2e42fa0c1162b.jpg","text":"Ayator is bursting with happiness.\nHe is joyful. Emotions come and go.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228054/size6/e3c53ed3340f0eeacb14e218a82e245f.jpg","text":"Hadiza is bored.\nShe needs to find something to do.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228056/size6/655dad5f8f4769ce21f602fe8baedff4.jpg","text":"Ayo is angry.\nHe is frustrated.\nAnger is a difficult feeling.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228057/size6/9b0c37a9fe736e74bbbc4490bd4745f8.jpg","text":"Labake is excited.\nWhat's the cause of her excitement?\nMother made her favourite food.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228058/size6/b1d11b938832a143378cd873ac24db3a.jpg","text":"Zege felt sleepy.\nHe was very tired.\n\"But wait, is 'sleepy' an emotion?\" asks Efe.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228059/size6/57386888e9c9f190882ccdbd3da82282.jpg","text":"Efe is confused!\nCan you answer his question?","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228060/size6/49f00f865bbbd2c6c756c5c7384f4d94.jpg","text":"Tega is feeling surprise and shock.\nHe heard some gossip. Is it true?","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228062/size6/3b8a815a29ac1319364736b7dbb655bd.jpg","text":"Yebo is sick.\nShe feels miserable.\nShe needs some medicine and rest to feel better.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228063/size6/453836e1142eaa810f8d41391cb817a7.jpg","text":"Sekyen is feeling content.\nShe has finished her chores.\nNow she can play.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228064/size6/d324fc4b01b340a00f8e8b158ad4eb12.jpg","text":"Vandefan does not have chores today.\nHe shows two thumbs up to Sekyen.\n\"Good job, now let's play!\" he says.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":217}}